T02D1935c:63a-1: krishna ya m'a ri kro dha r'a dza ba tra sa ra s'a dha nam n'a ma /
T02D1935c:63a-3: khro bo'i rgyal po gshin rje'i gshed nag po dus mthar phyin pa'i sgrub thabs zhes bya ba /
T02D1935c:63a-4: bcom ldan 'das gshin rje gshed la phyag 'tshal lo ;
T02D1935c:63a-5: / spros bral thugs su chud bdag 'gro ba kun khyab pa //
T02D1935c:63a-6: ma lus bdud 'joms thogs med khro bo kun gyi gtso //
T02D1935c:63a-7: padma rdo rje snyoms 'jug zhi bde mdzes pas bsgyings //
T02D1935c:63a-8: longs spyod rdzogs skur bzhengs pa'i snying po la btud de //
T02D1935c:63a-9: sangs rgyas thugs kyi rgyud rgyal 'bum pa thu bo che //
T02D1935c:63a-10: na da ku be ra la yab kyis rjes gdams shing //
T02D1935c:63a-11: de yis de nyid bsdus pa'i byang chub sems chen po'i //
T02D1935c:63a-12: rnam par rgyal ba gshed rgyud las byung bshad par bya //
T02D1935c:63a-13: 'gro kun sangs rgyas snying po ste //
T02D1935c:63a-14: gtso bo mi yang dad ldan brtan //
T02D1935c:63a-15: ral gri padma skyon med gnas //
T02D1935c:63a-16: cod pan brgyan pa mthong bar bya //
T02D1935c:63a-17: mtha' yang mi gnas gtso bo la //
T02D1935c:63a-18: dmigs dang padmos rjes bzung nas //
T02D1935c:63a-19: rgyal por dran pa byas nas kyang //
T02D1935c:63a-20: lhag pa'i lha rnams spyan drang ngo //
T02D1935c:63a-21: rnam dag bdun gyis sbyangs pa la //
T02D1935c:63a-22: tshangs pa bzhi yi sems gnas nas //
T02D1935c:63a-23: 'phrog pa med pa'i snying po nyid //
T02D1935c:63a-24: thog mtha' med pa dmigs par bya //
T02D1935c:63a-25: aom sh'u n+ya t'a dzny'a na badzra sva bh'a wa a'atma ko& ham /
T02D1935c:63a-26: yi ge gsum gyi rang bzhin ni //
T02D1935c:63a-27: bde gsal stong pa'i rang bzhin nyid //
T02D1935c:63a-28: thog mtha' med nas sems can la //
T02D1935c:63a-29: gnas phyir rig pa nyams mi bya //
T02D1935c:63a-30: h'um las re pha byung nas su //
T02D1935c:63b-0: nyi @63b dkyil rdo rje 'khor lo bsgom //
T02D1935c:63b-1: de rjes h'um las h'um byung ste //
T02D1935c:63b-2: rdo rje sems dpa' chos 'byung gnas //
T02D1935c:63b-3: sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgyar ldan //
T02D1935c:63b-4: padma rdo rjes mtshan byas pa'o //
T02D1935c:63b-5: gong mtshungs bhr'um las gzhal yas khang //
T02D1935c:63b-6: aom las rtag pa sna tshogs mnyam //
T02D1935c:63b-7: gdan ni rjes mthun gnas pa'o //
T02D1935c:63b-8: aa las mar ldan nyi ma zla //
T02D1935c:63b-9: mnyam pa h'um las rdo rje ste //
T02D1935c:63b-10: sku yi gzi brjid bsdus nga rgyal //
T02D1935c:63b-11: rgyud gshed rdo rje 'dzin pa bsgom //
T02D1935c:63b-12: phab pa'i sbyor ldan byang chub sems //
T02D1935c:63b-13: yongs 'gyur thabs dang shes rab sku //
T02D1935c:63b-14: yig 'bru lnga yis gang ba las //
T02D1935c:63b-15: 'phros pa'i lha mos bskul nas bzhengs //
T02D1935c:63b-16: chos kun bdag pos bsgom par bya //
T02D1935c:63b-17: aom dharma dh'a tu sva bh'a wa a'atma ko& ham /
T02D1935c:63b-18: ya las skyes pa'i gshin rje gshed //
T02D1935c:63b-20: g-yas dkar g-yon dmar phag mos 'khril //
T02D1935c:63b-21: ma he ser skya la bskum brkyang //
T02D1935c:63b-22: g-yas pa gri gug g-yon thod pa //
T02D1935c:63b-23: rdo rje ral gri 'khor lo pad //
T02D1935c:63b-24: thod pa lnga yis dbu brgyan cing //
T02D1935c:63b-25: dbu skyes gyen 'greng brgyad kyis brgyan //
T02D1935c:63b-27: me dpung nang na gnas par bsgom //
T02D1935c:63b-28: rang mtshungs ye shes sems dpa' ni //
T02D1935c:63b-29: cho ga gsum dang ldan pas so ;
T02D1935c:63b-30: / yi ge lnga rdzogs de bzhin gshegs //
T02D1935c:63b-31: rigs kyi mdog dang mtshun mar ldan //
T02D1935c:63b-32: sku ni mtho gang tshad yin te //
T02D1935c:63b-33: phra mo lnga ni tshon gang ngo //
T02D1935c:63b-34: sku gsum rab tu thob bya'i phyir //
T02D1935c:63b-35: lus ngag yid gsum byin brlab bya //
T02D1935c:63b-36: spyi gtsug rtag pa'i rgyal po ste //
T02D1935c:63b-37: mgrin par rdo rje nyi ma bsgom //
T02D1935c:63b-38: snying gar mi bskyod rdo rje 'chang //
T02D1935c:63b-40: mig la sa yi snying po ste //
T02D1935c:63b-41: rna ba la ni rdo rje 'dzin //
T02D1935c:63b-42: sna la nam mkha'i snying po mchog / lce la 'jig rten dbang phyug mgon //
T02D1935c:63b-43: sgrib pa rnam sel lus la dgod //
T02D1935c:63b-44: kun du bzang po yid kyi'o //
T02D1935c:63b-45: kshim dzim kham gam kam sam //
T02D1935c:63b-46: cho ga gsum dang ldan pa la //
T02D1935c:63b-47: aom dang h'um gis spel bar bya //
T02D1935c:63b-48: rdo rje lnga ni mchod byas la //
T02D1935c:63b-49: gsol btab dbang gis mi bskyod 'gyur //
T02D1935c:63b-50: mi bzad rdo rje 'khor lo nyid //
T02D1935c:63b-51: mchod bstod byas la dgug gzhug bya //
T02D1935c:63b-52: aom badzra sa tva sa ma ya /
T02D1935c:63b-53: tsakra mandala dh'a tu dza: h'um ba ho: sa ma ya stvam aa nya ham /
T02D1935c:64a-3: rdo rje nam mkha' byin rlabs la //
T02D1935c:64a-4: bskyod pas lnga 'gyur byang chub sems //
T02D1935c:64a-5: mkha' yi padmar rdzus skyes nas //
T02D1935c:64a-6: sa dgur bskyed la rab rgyas sku //
T02D1935c:64a-7: ba spu'i bu ga che nas spro //
T02D1935c:64a-8: sangs rgyas sprin yang rjes bsams nas //
T02D1935c:64a-9: rigs kyi don yang bsgrub par bya //
T02D1935c:64a-13: aom a'a ro lik me h'um /
T02D1935c:64a-14: aom pra dzny'a dhrik da h'um /
T02D1935c:64a-15: shar du gti mug gshed po ste //
T02D1935c:64a-16: lho ru nga rgyal gshed po'o //
T02D1935c:64a-17: nub tu 'dod chags gshed po ste //
T02D1935c:64a-18: byang du phrag dog gshed po'o //
T02D1935c:64a-19: shar la 'od zer gzhan rnon po //
T02D1935c:64a-20: dkar ser dmar ljang rang 'od rig / rigs kyi bdag po'i phyag rgya 'dzin //
T02D1935c:64a-21: gzhan ni go rims sbyor shes pa'o //
T02D1935c:64a-22: na yo n'i ra 'phros pa las //
T02D1935c:64a-23: byang chub sems kyis rab rgyas pa'i //
T02D1935c:64a-24: rtsa rtsi k'a sogs lha mo yis //
T02D1935c:64a-25: mchod pas rab tu mnyes par bya //
T02D1935c:64a-26: de nas rdo rje dril 'chang bas //
T02D1935c:64a-27: bstod pa yang ni ched du brjod //
T02D1935c:64a-28: dam tshig bzang po byin brlabs nas //
T02D1935c:64a-29: rdo rje h'um gis myang bar bya //
T02D1935c:64a-30: spro ba chen po 'jig rten khams //
T02D1935c:64a-31: thog ma med pas bsdus byas nas //
T02D1935c:64a-32: du mar brtson 'grus ldan yid kyis //
T02D1935c:64a-33: yang dang yang du goms par bya //
T02D1935c:64a-34: rdo rje snying ga'i dkyil 'khor la //
T02D1935c:64a-35: yid skyob bkod nas bzlas par bya //
T02D1935c:64a-36: aom hr'i: shtri: wi kri t'a na na h'um h'um phat phat /
T02D1935c:64a-37: rim dang cig car sbyor ba yi //
T02D1935c:64a-38: sems can don du bzlas par bya //
T02D1935c:64a-39: zla ba'o cog gi bcu bzhi la //
T02D1935c:64a-40: dri chus byugs pa'i dkyil 'khor ni //
T02D1935c:64a-41: gru gsum ldan zhing me tog spras //
T02D1935c:64a-42: mchod pa bzang ldan gtor mas bkang //
T02D1935c:64a-43: mi rus lnga bcu tham pa la //
T02D1935c:64a-44: khrag gi spangs pa'i mgo bor bsgom //
T02D1935c:64a-45: ri lu re la bshed nag phos //
T02D1935c:64a-46: brgyan pa khri yi bar du bzlas //
T02D1935c:64a-47: mchod pa rnams kyis mnyes byas la //
T02D1935c:64a-48: gsol btab gtor ma dur khrod sbyin //
T02D1935c:64a-60: ba su dha r'a ya phat /
T02D1935c:64a-61: be ma tsi tra ya sv'a /
T02D1935c:64a-64: phem phem phem phem phat sv'a h'a /
T02D1935c:64a-65: gad mo chen mo brgyad brgyad nas //
T02D1935c:64a-66: gnang ba byin nas gshegs par bsam //
T02D1935c:64b-1: srid pa gsum gyi 'khor lo ni //
T02D1935c:64b-2: dbang po skye mched stong pa yi //
T02D1935c:64b-3: lcags kyi khang pa bcu bdun gyi //
T02D1935c:64b-4: rdo rje snying po dgod par bya //
T02D1935c:64b-5: chu yi dkyil 'khor shing rta dang //
T02D1935c:64b-6: ce spyang rgyug pa lta bu'o //
T02D1935c:64b-7: sbyor ldan man ngag dam pa ni //
T02D1935c:64b-8: dam pa'i zhal las shes par bya //
T02D1935c:64b-10: gzhan du rgya cher bshad pas na //
T02D1935c:64b-11: 'dir ni mang du ma smos so //
T02D1935c:64b-12: ya ma r'a dza sa do me ya /
T02D1935c:64b-13: ya me do ru na yo da ya /
T02D1935c:64b-14: ya da yo ni ra ya kshe ya /
T02D1935c:64b-15: yakshe yatstsha ni r'a ma ya /
T02D1935c:64b-16: zhi ba'i mthar ni sv'a h'a /
T02D1935c:64b-17: rgyas dang dbang la aom dang ho //
T02D1935c:64b-18: drag po phat kyis brtan par bya //
T02D1935c:64b-20: rgyud dang bstan bcos mkhas pa bdag min te //
T02D1935c:64b-21: dam pa bla ma'i zhabs la brten nas chos 'di byas //
T02D1935c:64b-22: rgyud kyi mngon rtogs nges par byin pa'i yon tan dpal //
T02D1935c:64b-23: dang dang shes rab snying rjer bcas rnams nges sgrol shog / bsnyen dang sgrub pa'i cho ga'i rim //
T02D1935c:64b-24: zab mo'i sgrub pa rnyed dka' ba //
T02D1935c:64b-25: nor bu lta bu'i gzhung 'di yis //
T02D1935c:64b-26: 'gro kun gshin rje gshed nag shog / khro bo'i
T02D1935c:64b-27: rgyal po gshin rje gshed nag po'i dus mthar phyin
T02D1935c:64b-28: pa'i sgrub pa'i thabs zhes bya ba rdzogs so /
T02D1935c:64b-30: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po shr'i pandi tas mdzad pa'o //
